{"tid":1644482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大家勸下富臨唔好交贖款比黑警呀","createTime":"2019-10-10T14:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:14:54.000Z","uid":254452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c85ecac9506ad6e7ee9a87a5ac4515459e41d89","tid":1644482,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">修例風波：富臨集團收自稱反修例組織電郵索款</span><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5StC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=cd8cb017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】反修例風波令不少商戶受牽連。據了解，一個自稱會「用一切可能的手段守護香港的民主和自由」的組織負責人，上月下旬發電郵予富臨集團，聲言有人建議組織對該集團「實施毀滅性打擊」，但願意給予對方「一次贖罪機會」，只要在收郵件後10天內對該組織「捐贈」「一筆款項」，就可以「既往不咎」。<br />\n<br />\n電郵中，該名自稱負責人稱，他們的組織只接受比特幣「捐款」，現時一個比特幣市價約8萬港元，「捐款」並無上限，但不可低於0.1個比特幣，又指如10天內收不到款項，組織就會「嚴懲」該個集團。<br />\n<br />\n根據該封電郵，該名自稱負責人形容他們的組織「儆惡懲奸，但並非一言堂」，而他們是行動者，為達目的不惜代價，在是次反修例事件中，該組織的「手足」一直「衝在最前綫(線)」，「以鮮血和汗水踐行自己的誓言」。<br />\n<br />\n富臨集團回覆東網查詢時表示，有關事件已轉交警方處理，暫不方便回應任何問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E6%94%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E7%B4%A2%E6%AC%BE-103205464.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%2587%25A8%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2583%25B5%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E6%25AC%25BE-103205464.html&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5StC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=ab46a083\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E6%94%B6%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E7%B4%A2%E6%AC%BE-103205464.html</a><br />\n<br />\n因為純學術分析,你交完錢都係會繼續比人裝修,慳番D錢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010b01749513f87eb0a0b0be4ffe4e3c9d5987fd","tid":1644482,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"係咪喬裝 IT 狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1436bbb32d3d0638771363a56970fb92db6971","tid":1644482,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"010b01749513f87eb0a0b0be4ffe4e3c9d5987fd","tid":1644482,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"係咪喬裝 IT 狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"今次肯定係,唔洗審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由商業罪案調查科喬裝"}]}